        "TileImage": "$($repository 0537209e-960f-4686-a9b4-65fe67bee060).Image",
        "Description": "This version of Bangkok is better than its morning variation due to the added minor NPCs area on the fourth level. For this mission, I have employed a specially routed NPC. When they are reaching their intended location, this NPC presents many kill windows for the observant. However, once they have arrived at their destination, creativity is required to eliminate them successfully. I have previously considered these NPCs for Paris, but find their appearance here to be better.",
